    the have been recorded are used in these reports. The reports require a start and end date for which
    to calculate the costs in that period. By default, the start date will be set to the first of the
    current month and the end date will be set to the current date. As with the job reports, items are
    grouped by category for ease of reading and finding specific items.
</p>
<p>
    There are three types of charge reports: plant charges for a specific job, inventory charges for a
    specific job, and a financial summary of all current jobs. All of these reports depend upon a specified
    date range.
</p>
